snippet.title: Trash Panda Release Trailer
snippet.description:
New trailer! Launch date set! Trash Panda is ready for the world!!!
If you're in #Toronto, come to the launch party on November 15th, and join the countdown to going live! 

Free admission, RSVP here:
https://tickettailor.com/events/jleaverpresentations/1056439

Wishlist on 
@Steam: 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1669320/Trash_Panda
